name: ET Jump - Endless Free Jump Game
name_original: ET Jump - Endless Free Jump Game
description:
Are you all set to take off on an epic Jumping journey with ET jump?

Explore a new world amidst your journey. Collect coins, Power ups and dodge Aliens with your power. ET Jump has it all!!
Experience stunning and never seen graphics as you move high.

Key Features:
* 100+ incredible levels to pass by and reach to a point where you can explore a new world.
* Power Ups, boosts - grab as much as you can and use them to the full extent.
* Kill the Aliens/monsters with your special powers.
* Unlock new characters - BaitZy, E.J and CYphEr. check them and their special Powers.
* Jump High with Jumpy shoes, Fly high with extreme Jump & grab coins with Magnet.
* Submit score on Facebook, Twitter & Instagram and earn free coins.
* Global leader-boards and achievement!

*****************
How to Play:
1. Login to Game Center and play the Game for Maximum benefits.

2. Tilt to move left/right, jump on the bars and grab coins to move high, tap the screen to shoot the aliens.
*****************
Note: ET Jump is insanely addictive!!
